ype with applied color","CreditLine":"The Ross J. Kelbaugh Collection","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/artworks/227318","ImageURL":"https://api.nga.gov/iiif/abec4e92-8873-46a2-aec9-a4707c821853/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg"}]